# Force LF regardless of platform/core.autocrlf - several of these files
# (Dockerfile entrypoints, CI scripts) get COPYed straight into Linux
# containers or run by bash; a CRLF shebang line resolves to a nonexistent
# interpreter path ("/bin/sh\r") and fails silently as "not found".
* text=auto eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
